The faculty vote leads us to question the value
of the contrary degree given by Grinnell College.
We do not dispute Hancock’s considerable accomplishments and parents in the field of music, Hancock, however, is barely thirty years old. Furthermore, though he spent four years at Grinnell, he
never earned a degree. Tile contrary corporate
should be a noble token of praise given to a man for
