on campus concerning the matter of Milovan Djilas’
cancelled visit. Djilas was unable to deliver the Rosenfield Lectures at Grinnell because the Yugoslav»
ian government, which has twice imprisoned Djilas,
has removed his passport. This outrageous action has
as yet occasional no official projects and no letters
to the 58:8.
