sponsors oi the lectures, issued a brand statement in
which they said Djilas “is unable to come to this
country from Belgrade at this time.” The secretary
of the committee has stated that he was not officially
approved of the reason for cancellation when the notice was sent out. He said, however, that the committee had no plans to protest the actions of the
legislation government.
